{"tid":633498,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國電影攝影蓬勃　產生著作鄰接權　香港二創蓬勃　產生二次創作權","createTime":"2018-04-18T11:15:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T14:56:36.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9c0f553b32339eba5d91c9024ecc9e4744012a88","tid":633498,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T11:15:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/978938343466532864\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F978938343466532864&d=HeqzSylQ9iSvFK7c0P5NN0jIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=57291d16\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F978938343466532864&h=1cb9d120\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/978938343466532864</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/979015250333777920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F979015250333777920&d=HeqzSylQ9iSvFK7c0P5NN0jIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=f9e2eb43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F979015250333777920&h=ddcca83b\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/979015250333777920</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/979016672240533504\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F979016672240533504&d=HeqzSylQ9iSvFK7c0P5NN0jIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=2eebc26a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FZenoIndie%2Fstatus%2F979016672240533504&h=7a70ec80\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ZenoIndie/status/979016672240533504</a><br />\n<br />\n其實香港不是反對版權。那是相似的，印刷術誕生，出版蓬勃，產生了版權，在法國，電影、攝影蓬勃，出現了著作鄰接權的需求，而香港因為二創蓬勃，所以出現了二次創作權的需求。<br />\n<br />\n大型電視台正式播的改詞經典《幾許瘋語》、《蝕到空虛》。英國國歌和中國國歌都有傳統改詞惡搞版。改詞搞笑歌可以出碟大賣，出系列。天皇巨星雲集演出二創笑片。互聯網進一步爆發，大量改圖、「潮文」、改詞、配音二創，網民集體二次創作模式，香港本地論壇才有的創意台（創意板）。<br />\n<br />\n電視廣告說創業是香港人的基因，倒不如說創意是香港人的基因。喜歡二次創作，不但生活自娛，更是經濟，運用於政治，甚至說是香港民族的獨特民族性也不為過。"},{"pid":"82303b892bbae6c72987fb440ddc59b5cc5b9ec6","tid":633498,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T11:27:11.000Z","msg":"賊：我只系劫富濟貧<br />\n<br />\n賊：我貧，所以濟自己<br />\n<br />\n賊：與其說劫富濟貧，不如說有效運用資源，反正有錢佬駛唔曬"},{"pid":"5223ca334cd0b9b604914e15d9411bb08a26c586","tid":633498,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:56:36.000Z","msg":"回錯post？"}]}